ygData.messageBody:
Yes, I actually play exclusively on Brell except when the server is down. Now I
am back from vacation, look for my Dedric character ( lvl 10.999 Gnome Necro.
Was lvl 11 till Minotaur Hero killed me). Also, I saw several others on over the
weekend. Also, the list owner is on apparently 24/7 :) Her Luna character hit
lvl 24 (maybe higher today??) so she is on plenty of the time.

Hope to meet you in EQ soon.
